sure\nand correct for both turbulence and fragmentation effects and will eventually\nrestore the full capability and spatial resolution of the future ELT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 08:14:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-20"}
