nds only on the confinement length scale along the\nfeedback direction. The broader marginal probability distribution accredits the\nincreased average displacement in a cycle and the lower efficacy in an\nentropy-dominated system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 08:57:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
