athbb{R}^2$\nare totally new, especially the results on bi-spatial random attractors and\nstochastic Liouville type theorem for 2D SNSE with linear multiplicative noise\nare obtained in any kind of domains for the first time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 10:52:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Feb 2023 11:16:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-06"}
