ant problem. The mass\ndensity of the $\\Omega(1)$ and $\\Omega(2)$ substrata is equivalent to that of\naround $3$ protons contained in a box with a volume of $1$ cubic metre.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 14:15:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-22"}
